<h2><strong>CADmeister2020 Version Upgrade (MOLD)</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;MOLD-CREATOR&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>1.&nbsp;Expansion of parting creation function</strong></h4><h5>-&nbsp;PL Curve improvement</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;The functions are enhanced to specify locations where there are gaps caused by irregular shaping.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_1.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h5>- PL Surface improvement</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;We have enhanced the functions to deal with Corner Parts and adjacency between (adjacent) surfaces.&nbsp;</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_1.2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>2.&nbsp;Ejector pin placement function</strong></h4><h5>-&nbsp;Functions related to Ejector Pins/E Pins</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;We added the functions to position Ejector Pins. We also enhanced the operability.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_2.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h5>-&nbsp;Create and Edit E Pin Symbols</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;We have added symbol capabilities to help considerations about E Pin positions.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_2.2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h5>-&nbsp;Place and Edit E Pin</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;An one-time 3D visualization for positioned E Pin symbols is now enabled. The E Pin positions can be edited on the 3D screens.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_2.3.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>3.&nbsp;User-defined parts that use family tables</strong></h4><h5><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>User-defined parts using family tables</h5><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_3.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h5>-&nbsp;User-defined parts using family tables</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;We have added the function to set a formula through the use of a Family Table.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_3.2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull; CAE-MOLD&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>4. Improvement of Analysis Result Display</strong></h4><h5><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Display Analysis Result / isosurface display</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;We have enhanced the &ldquo;DisplayAnalysisResult&rdquo; command to display CAE analysis results. The command window can now display isosurfaces.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_4.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;FORM-EX &bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>5.&nbsp;Preliminary measures for warp deformation</strong></h4><h5>-&nbsp;FORM-EX (probable deformation support fonction)</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;FORX-EX quickly and highly precisely models for shaping and models by executing the &ldquo;Forming&rdquo; command on the basis of material characteristics data and STL figure data. &nbsp;FORM-EX helps users to shorten delivery durations.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_5.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h5>-&nbsp;FORM-EX（Functions to Support the &ldquo;Forming&rdquo; Command)</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;FORM-EX enables preparatory countermeasures to deal with Warpage Deformation to be induced by shaping.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_5.2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;Easy-Modeling &bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>6.&nbsp;Strengthening of Draft function</strong></h4><h5>-<strong>&nbsp;</strong>The &ldquo;DraftingSrf&rdquo; Command</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;We have enhanced the &ldquo;DraftingSrf&rdquo; command with the processing function to embed.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_6.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>7.&nbsp;Two-stage extension surface</strong></h4><h5>-&nbsp;The &ldquo;2StepExtendedSurface&rdquo; Command</h5><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;We have added the function to extend a surface in two precision degrees.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/MOLD/CADmeister2020_Mold_7.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p>